{"about_the_game":"Return to the world of Slaughter, a gloomy place where anarchy and lawlessness reign. Reckless bandits and thugs have broken free from a massive prison, forming gangs and engaging in fierce battles to gain control over the territory.<br />\r\nOur hero - Russell, found himself in the very middle of this chaos and is trying to survive at any cost. He is destined for the fate of a slave if he does not find a way to get out of prison.<br />\r\nRussell has to arm himself and carve his way to freedom. Along the journey, the player, alongside the main character, will discover what is unfolding in this strange place \u2014 encountering allies and unraveling the dark secrets concealed within the vast complex's walls.<br />\r\nFate has tossed you right into the turf of the deadliest and savage thugs. Well, it's too bad for those sorry bastards. Arm yourself, soldier, and rid this hornet's nest. Zero tolerance for those scumbags - there will be enough bullets for everyone.<br />\r\nExplore the vast complex, discover detours, find weapons and upgrade equipment, study documents and diaries that shed light on what is happening around.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSlaughter: The Lost Outpost is the third-person shooter with metroidvania elements. You have to explore large and intricate levels and find a way to freedom.<br />\r\n- Intense battles with dangerous enemies, each of which requires a unique strategic approach.<br />\r\n- Large and varied levels with many hiding places and detours.<br />\r\n- The search for various weapons and equipment will significantly impact gameplay.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1704783372","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584050/page.bg.jpg?t=1704783372","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584050/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1704783372","capsule_imagev5":"https